    • Method Detail

      • getIncludePath

        public java.nio.file.Path getIncludePath()
        Get path to use as an include path to get access to the files in the tree. If getHeaderMap() is present, then the path it returns needs to be passed as an include path as well and it has to be passed before the path returned from this method.

      • getSystemIncludePath

        public java.nio.file.Path getSystemIncludePath()
        Get path to use as a system include path to get access to the files in the tree. As opposed to getIncludePath(), this method does not require any other include paths to be used.

      • getHeaderMap

        Get path of the header map indexing this tree if one exists.
